# Lab Mobile App - Complete Data Structure

## TAB 1: PATIENTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| patient_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique patient identifier | P001, P002 |
| full_name | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Patient's full name | John Doe |
| date_of_birth | DATE | Yes | Date of birth | 1990-05-15 |
| gender | VARCHAR(10) | Yes | Gender (Male/Female/Other) | Male |
| phone | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Contact phone number | +1234567890 |
| email | VARCHAR(100) | No | Email address | john@example.com |
| address | TEXT | No | Full address | 123 Main St, City |
| emergency_contact | VARCHAR(20) | No | Emergency contact number | +1234567891 |
| medical_history | TEXT | No | Medical history notes | Diabetes, Hypertension |
| blood_type | VARCHAR(5) | No | Blood type | A+, B-, O+ |
| insurance_info | TEXT | No | Insurance details | Blue Cross, Policy#123 |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 2: TESTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| test_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique test identifier | T001, T002 |
| patient_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to patient | P001 |
| test_type | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Type of test | Blood Test, Urine Analysis |
| test_name | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Specific test name | CBC, Lipid Profile |
| description | TEXT | No | Test description | Complete Blood Count |
| price | DECIMAL(10,2) | Yes | Test price | 150.00 |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Test status | Pending, In Progress, Completed |
| priority | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Priority level | Normal, Urgent, Emergency |
| ordered_by | VARCHAR(100) | No | Doctor who ordered | Dr. Smith |
| ordered_date | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Order date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| completed_date | TIMESTAMP | No | Completion date | 2024-01-01 15:00:00 |
| results | TEXT | No | Test results summary | Normal, Abnormal |
| notes | TEXT | No | Additional notes | Patient fasting required |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 3: TEST_RESULTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| result_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique result identifier | R001, R002 |
| test_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to test | T001 |
| parameter | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Test parameter name | Hemoglobin, WBC |
| value | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Test result value | 14.5, 7500 |
| unit | VARCHAR(20) | No | Unit of measurement | g/dL, cells/μL |
| reference_range | VARCHAR(50) | No | Normal range | 12.0-16.0, 4500-11000 |
| is_abnormal | BOOLEAN | Yes | Abnormal flag | true, false |
| notes | TEXT | No | Result notes | Slightly elevated |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 4: APPOINTMENTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| appointment_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique appointment identifier | A001, A002 |
| patient_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to patient | P001 |
| appointment_date | DATE | Yes | Appointment date | 2024-01-01 |
| appointment_time | TIME | Yes | Appointment time | 10:00:00 |
| test_type | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Type of test | Blood Test |
| doctor_name | VARCHAR(100) | No | Doctor name | Dr. Smith |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Appointment status | Scheduled, Completed |
| notes | TEXT | No | Appointment notes | Fasting required |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 5: PAYMENTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| payment_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique payment identifier | PAY001, PAY002 |
| test_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to test | T001 |
| amount | DECIMAL(10,2) | Yes | Payment amount | 150.00 |
| payment_method | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Payment method | Cash, Card, Insurance |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Payment status | Pending, Completed |
| transaction_id | VARCHAR(50) | No | Transaction reference | TXN123456 |
| payment_date | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Payment date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| notes | TEXT | No | Payment notes | Insurance claim pending |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 6: USERS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| user_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique user identifier | U001, U002 |
| username | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Username for login | admin, doctor1 |
| email | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Email address | admin@lab.com |
| full_name | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Full name | John Admin |
| role | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | User role | Admin, Doctor, Technician |
| is_active | BOOLEAN | Yes | Active status | true, false |
| last_login | TIMESTAMP | No | Last login date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 7: REPORT_TEMPLATES
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| template_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique template identifier | TEMP001 |
| name | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Template name | CBC Report Template |
| test_type | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Associated test type | Blood Test (CBC) |
| description | TEXT | No | Template description | Complete Blood Count Report |
| header_template | TEXT | No | Report header template | COMPLETE BLOOD COUNT |
| footer_template | TEXT | No | Report footer template | Reviewed by: {doctor} |
| is_active | BOOLEAN | Yes | Active status | true, false |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 8: REPORT_FIELDS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| field_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique field identifier | FIELD001 |
| template_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to template | TEMP001 |
| name | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Field name | hemoglobin, wbc |
| label | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Display label | Hemoglobin, White Blood Cells |
| type | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Field type | number, text, textarea |
| unit | VARCHAR(20) | No | Unit of measurement | g/dL, cells/μL |
| normal_range | VARCHAR(50) | No | Normal range | 12.0-16.0, 4500-11000 |
| default_value | VARCHAR(50) | No | Default value | 0, Normal |
| is_required | BOOLEAN | Yes | Required field | true, false |
| order | INTEGER | Yes | Display order | 1, 2, 3 |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 9: REPORTS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| report_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique report identifier | REP001 |
| test_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to test | T001 |
| template_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Reference to template | TEMP001 |
| patient_name | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Patient name | John Doe |
| test_type | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Test type | Blood Test (CBC) |
| test_date | DATE | Yes | Test date | 2024-01-01 |
| field_values | JSON | Yes | Field values | {"hemoglobin": "14.5", "wbc": "7500"} |
| doctor_name | VARCHAR(100) | No | Doctor name | Dr. Smith |
| technician_name | VARCHAR(100) | No | Technician name | Tech Johnson |
| status | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Report status | Draft, Completed |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 10: SETTINGS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| setting_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique setting identifier | SET001 |
| setting_key | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Setting key | lab_name, contact_info |
| setting_value | TEXT | Yes | Setting value | "Saied Lab", "Contact details" |
| setting_type | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Value type | string, number, boolean |
| description | TEXT | No | Setting description | Laboratory name |
| is_active | BOOLEAN | Yes | Active status | true, false |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Record creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| updated_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Last update date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 11: AUDIT_LOGS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| log_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique log identifier | LOG001 |
| user_id | VARCHAR(20) | No | User who performed action | U001 |
| action | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Action performed | CREATE, UPDATE, DELETE |
| table_name | VARCHAR(50) | Yes | Table affected | patients, tests |
| record_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Record identifier | P001, T001 |
| old_values | JSON | No | Previous values | {"name": "John"} |
| new_values | JSON | No | New values | {"name": "John Doe"} |
| ip_address | VARCHAR(45) | No | IP address | 192.168.1.1 |
| user_agent | TEXT | No | User agent string | Mozilla/5.0... |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Log creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |

## TAB 12: NOTIFICATIONS
| Field Name | Data Type | Required | Description | Example |
|------------|-----------|----------|-------------|---------|
| notification_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Unique notification identifier | NOT001 |
| user_id | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Target user | U001 |
| title | VARCHAR(100) | Yes | Notification title | Test Results Ready |
| message | TEXT | Yes | Notification message | Test results for patient John Doe |
| type | VARCHAR(20) | Yes | Notification type | info, warning, error |
| is_read | BOOLEAN | Yes | Read status | false, true |
| related_id | VARCHAR(20) | No | Related record | T001 |
| related_type | VARCHAR(20) | No | Related table | tests |
| created_at | TIMESTAMP | Yes | Creation date | 2024-01-01 10:00:00 |
| read_at | TIMESTAMP | No | Read date | 2024-01-01 11:00:00 |
